Package org.daiitech.naftah.parser.time

Class DefaultArabicDateParserVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
org.daiitech.naftah.parser.ArabicDateParserBaseVisitor<Object>
org.daiitech.naftah.parser.time.DefaultArabicDateParserVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<Object>, ArabicDateParserVisitor<Object>
public class DefaultArabicDateParserVisitor extends ArabicDateParserBaseVisitor<Object>
A default visitor implementation for parsing Arabic date and time expressions.

This class extends ArabicDateParserBaseVisitor and provides implementations for converting parse tree nodes into corresponding ArabicTemporal objects, such as ArabicDate, ArabicTime, and ArabicDateTime.

It handles:

  • Date and calendar specifiers
  • Time with optional AM/PM markers
  • Time zones or offsets
  • Integration of date and time into a single temporal object

Author:
Chakib Daii
